<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<jmeterTestPlan version="1.2" properties="5.0" jmeter="5.6.3">
  <hashTree>
    <TestPlan guiclass="TestPlanGui" testclass="TestPlan" testname="F009 Write-Read Race Reproduction Test">
      <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">F009 Write-Read 경합 재현 테스트.

목적: Redis Hash/ZSet 순차 쓰기 중간 상태를 Reader가 관찰하는지 확인.

전제조건:
1. spring.profiles.active=f009-test 로 애플리케이션 기동
2. RDBMS에 F009 테스트 매물 3건 + REVIEW_STATISTICS 3건 삽입 완료
3. Redis에 Hash, ZSet, bounds, safety 데이터 주입 완료
4. JWT_TOKEN 변수에 유효한 인증 토큰 설정

판정 기준:
- Reader 응답에 F009_TARGET_A0000000000000000000 포함 AND price=80000 → 재현 성공
- 요청 budgetMax=60000인데 deposit=80000 매물이 응답에 포함 = 금지 상태

타이밍:
- Writer가 syncAwait()에 도달하는 데 약 100ms 소요
- Reader의 Constant Timer 2000ms는 Writer latch 도달에 충분한 마진 제공
- syncAwait() timeout 30초 이내에 Reader가 releaseWriterIfTargetIncluded() 호출 필요
- 2000ms + 25개 자치구 순회 시간 ≪ 30초이므로 안전</stringProp>
      <elementProp name="TestPlan.user_defined_variables" elementType="Arguments" guiclass="ArgumentsPanel" testclass="Arguments">
        <collectionProp name="Arguments.arguments">
          <elementProp name="HOST" elementType="Argument">
            <stringProp name="Argument.name">HOST</stringProp>
            <stringProp name="Argument.value">localhost</stringProp>
            <stringProp name="Argument.metadata">=</stringProp>
          </elementProp>
          <elementProp name="PORT" elementType="Argument">
            <stringProp name="Argument.name">PORT</stringProp>
            <stringProp name="Argument.value">8185</stringProp>
            <stringProp name="Argument.metadata">=</stringProp>
          </elementProp>
          <elementProp name="JWT_TOKEN" elementType="Argument">
            <stringProp name="Argument.name">JWT_TOKEN</stringProp>
            <stringProp name="Argument.value">eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6Inloamo4MTUiLCJ1c2VySWQiOiJ5aGpqODE1Iiwicm9sZXMiOlsiUk9MRV9VU0VSIl0sImlhdCI6MTc3ODIxMTE4NCwiZXhwIjoxNzc4MjE0Nzg0fQ.tC3pwd5KGHqqm7mitSo6q4CEmHbaCfJi6BOdMKtLnoY</stringProp>
            <stringProp name="Argument.metadata">=</stringProp>
          </elementProp>
        </collectionProp>
      </elementProp>
    </TestPlan>
    <hashTree>
      <ThreadGroup guiclass="ThreadGroupGui" testclass="ThreadGroup" testname="Thread Group 1 — Writer (매물 수정)">
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.num_threads">1</intProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.ramp_time">0</intProp>
        <longProp name="ThreadGroup.delay">0</longProp>
        <boolProp name="ThreadGroup.same_user_on_next_iteration">true</boolProp>
        <stringProp name="ThreadGroup.on_sample_error">continue</stringProp>
        <elementProp name="ThreadGroup.main_controller" elementType="LoopController" guiclass="LoopControlPanel" testclass="LoopController">
          <stringProp name="LoopController.loops">1</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="LoopController.continue_forever">false</boolProp>
        </elementProp>
      </ThreadGroup>
      <hashTree>
        <HeaderManager guiclass="HeaderPanel" testclass="HeaderManager" testname="HTTP Header Manager" enabled="true">
          <collectionProp name="HeaderManager.headers">
            <elementProp name="" elementType="Header">
              <stringProp name="Header.name">Content-Type</stringProp>
              <stringProp name="Header.value">application/json</stringProp>
            </elementProp>
            <elementProp name="" elementType="Header">
              <stringProp name="Header.name">Cookie</stringProp>
              <stringProp name="Header.value">Authorization=${JWT_TOKEN}</stringProp>
            </elementProp>
          </collectionProp>
        </HeaderManager>
        <hashTree/>
        <HTTPSamplerProxy guiclass="HttpTestSampleGui" testclass="HTTPSamplerProxy" testname="PATCH 매물 수정 — deposit 50000→80000">
          <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">Writer 요청.
syncRedisAfterUpdate()에서 Hash putAll 직후 syncAwait()에 의해 정지.
Reader가 releaseWriterIfTargetIncluded()를 호출할 때까지 대기.
response_timeout=60000ms: latch 30초 + 후속 처리 마진.</stringProp>
          <intProp name="HTTPSampler.connect_timeout">5000</intProp>
          <intProp name="HTTPSampler.response_timeout">60000</intProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.domain">${HOST}</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.port">${PORT}</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.protocol">http</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.path">/wherehouse/api/v1/properties/charter/F009_TARGET_A0000000000000000000</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="HTTPSampler.follow_redirects">true</boolProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.method">PATCH</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="HTTPSampler.use_keepalive">true</boolProp>
          <boolProp name="HTTPSampler.postBodyRaw">true</boolProp>
          <elementProp name="HTTPsampler.Arguments" elementType="Arguments">
            <collectionProp name="Arguments.arguments">
              <elementProp name="" elementType="HTTPArgument">
                <boolProp name="HTTPArgument.always_encode">false</boolProp>
                <stringProp name="Argument.value">{&#xd;
  &quot;deposit&quot;: 80000&#xd;
}</stringProp>
                <stringProp name="Argument.metadata">=</stringProp>
              </elementProp>
            </collectionProp>
          </elementProp>
        </HTTPSamplerProxy>
        <hashTree/>
        <ResultCollector guiclass="ViewResultsFullVisualizer" testclass="ResultCollector" testname="View Results Tree — Writer">
          <boolProp name="ResultCollector.error_logging">false</boolProp>
          <objProp>
            <name>saveConfig</name>
            <value class="SampleSaveConfiguration">
              <time>true</time>
              <latency>true</latency>
              <timestamp>true</timestamp>
              <success>true</success>
              <label>true</label>
              <code>true</code>
              <message>true</message>
              <threadName>true</threadName>
              <dataType>true</dataType>
              <encoding>false</encoding>
              <assertions>true</assertions>
              <subresults>true</subresults>
              <responseData>true</responseData>
              <samplerData>true</samplerData>
              <xml>false</xml>
              <fieldNames>true</fieldNames>
              <responseHeaders>true</responseHeaders>
              <requestHeaders>true</requestHeaders>
              <responseDataOnError>false</responseDataOnError>
              <saveAssertionResultsFailureMessage>true</saveAssertionResultsFailureMessage>
              <assertionsResultsToSave>0</assertionsResultsToSave>
              <bytes>true</bytes>
              <sentBytes>true</sentBytes>
              <url>true</url>
              <threadCounts>true</threadCounts>
              <idleTime>true</idleTime>
              <connectTime>true</connectTime>
            </value>
          </objProp>
          <stringProp name="filename"></stringProp>
        </ResultCollector>
        <hashTree/>
      </hashTree>
      <ThreadGroup guiclass="ThreadGroupGui" testclass="ThreadGroup" testname="Thread Group 2 — Reader (추천 조회)">
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.num_threads">1</intProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.ramp_time">0</intProp>
        <longProp name="ThreadGroup.delay">0</longProp>
        <boolProp name="ThreadGroup.same_user_on_next_iteration">true</boolProp>
        <stringProp name="ThreadGroup.on_sample_error">continue</stringProp>
        <elementProp name="ThreadGroup.main_controller" elementType="LoopController" guiclass="LoopControlPanel" testclass="LoopController">
          <stringProp name="LoopController.loops">1</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="LoopController.continue_forever">false</boolProp>
        </elementProp>
      </ThreadGroup>
      <hashTree>
        <HeaderManager guiclass="HeaderPanel" testclass="HeaderManager" testname="HTTP Header Manager">
          <collectionProp name="HeaderManager.headers">
            <elementProp name="" elementType="Header">
              <stringProp name="Header.name">Content-Type</stringProp>
              <stringProp name="Header.value">application/json</stringProp>
            </elementProp>
            <elementProp name="" elementType="Header">
              <stringProp name="Header.name">Cookie</stringProp>
              <stringProp name="Header.value">Authorization=${JWT_TOKEN}</stringProp>
            </elementProp>
          </collectionProp>
        </HeaderManager>
        <hashTree/>
        <ConstantTimer guiclass="ConstantTimerGui" testclass="ConstantTimer" testname="Constant Timer — Writer latch 도달 대기">
          <stringProp name="ConstantTimer.delay">2000</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">Writer가 syncAwait()에 도달하는 데 약 100ms 소요.
2000ms는 충분한 마진을 제공하여 Reader 요청 시점에
Hash 신값 + ZSet 구값 중간 상태가 확실히 형성되도록 한다.</stringProp>
        </ConstantTimer>
        <hashTree/>
        <HTTPSamplerProxy guiclass="HttpTestSampleGui" testclass="HTTPSamplerProxy" testname="POST 추천 조회 — 전세 지역구">
          <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">Reader 요청.
budgetMax=60000 조건으로 조회.
재현 성공 시 F009_TARGET_A0000000000000000000(deposit=80000)가 응답에 포함됨.</stringProp>
          <intProp name="HTTPSampler.connect_timeout">5000</intProp>
          <intProp name="HTTPSampler.response_timeout">60000</intProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.domain">${HOST}</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.port">${PORT}</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.protocol">http</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.path">/wherehouse/api/recommendations/charter-districts</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="HTTPSampler.follow_redirects">true</boolProp>
          <stringProp name="HTTPSampler.method">POST</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="HTTPSampler.use_keepalive">true</boolProp>
          <boolProp name="HTTPSampler.postBodyRaw">true</boolProp>
          <elementProp name="HTTPsampler.Arguments" elementType="Arguments">
            <collectionProp name="Arguments.arguments">
              <elementProp name="" elementType="HTTPArgument">
                <boolProp name="HTTPArgument.always_encode">false</boolProp>
                <stringProp name="Argument.value">{&#xd;
  &quot;budgetMin&quot;: 40000,&#xd;
  &quot;budgetMax&quot;: 60000,&#xd;
  &quot;areaMin&quot;: 20.0,&#xd;
  &quot;areaMax&quot;: 40.0,&#xd;
  &quot;priority1&quot;: &quot;PRICE&quot;,&#xd;
  &quot;priority2&quot;: &quot;SAFETY&quot;,&#xd;
  &quot;priority3&quot;: &quot;SPACE&quot;,&#xd;
  &quot;budgetFlexibility&quot;: 0,&#xd;
  &quot;minSafetyScore&quot;: 0,&#xd;
  &quot;absoluteMinArea&quot;: 0.0&#xd;
}</stringProp>
                <stringProp name="Argument.metadata">=</stringProp>
              </elementProp>
            </collectionProp>
          </elementProp>
        </HTTPSamplerProxy>
        <hashTree/>
        <ResultCollector guiclass="ViewResultsFullVisualizer" testclass="ResultCollector" testname="View Results Tree — Reader">
          <boolProp name="ResultCollector.error_logging">false</boolProp>
          <objProp>
            <name>saveConfig</name>
            <value class="SampleSaveConfiguration">
              <time>true</time>
              <latency>true</latency>
              <timestamp>true</timestamp>
              <success>true</success>
              <label>true</label>
              <code>true</code>
              <message>true</message>
              <threadName>true</threadName>
              <dataType>true</dataType>
              <encoding>false</encoding>
              <assertions>true</assertions>
              <subresults>true</subresults>
              <responseData>true</responseData>
              <samplerData>true</samplerData>
              <xml>false</xml>
              <fieldNames>true</fieldNames>
              <responseHeaders>true</responseHeaders>
              <requestHeaders>true</requestHeaders>
              <responseDataOnError>false</responseDataOnError>
              <saveAssertionResultsFailureMessage>true</saveAssertionResultsFailureMessage>
              <assertionsResultsToSave>0</assertionsResultsToSave>
              <bytes>true</bytes>
              <sentBytes>true</sentBytes>
              <url>true</url>
              <threadCounts>true</threadCounts>
              <idleTime>true</idleTime>
              <connectTime>true</connectTime>
            </value>
          </objProp>
          <stringProp name="filename"></stringProp>
        </ResultCollector>
        <hashTree/>
      </hashTree>
    </hashTree>
  </hashTree>
</jmeterTestPlan>
